      • flatTransformEach

        public static <OUT,IN> TransformerUtils.Transformer<List<OUT>,Iterable<IN>> flatTransformEach(Transformer<? extends Iterable<OUT>,? super IN> mapper)
        Adapts an flat element mapper to transform each elements individually of the collection. The result will apply a proper flatMap algorithm to the provided collection.
        Type Parameters:
        OUT - output element type resulting from the transform
        IN - input element type to transform
        Parameters:
        mapper - an element mapper
        Returns:
        a TransformerUtils.Transformer instance to flat transform each the element of an iterable, never null.
